{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775882025270,"sessionID":"ses_2853214c7ffe3yLhm2xnrqV65c","part":{"id":"prt_d7ad1381a001L1PISeMz2jLAV8","messageID":"msg_d7acf54d8001k2hvkR3F6RTl2B","sessionID":"ses_2853214c7ffe3yLhm2xnrqV65c","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-1fa160d37fc4446988b7f6d4364028de","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# Delta Specification: AR-029 вҖ” SDK HTTP еә•еұӮе®ўжҲ·з«Ҝ\n\n**Module:** sdk-python  \n**Language:** Python  \n**Size:** M\n\n---\n\n## Purpose\n\nдёә AgentCube Python SDK е®һзҺ°з»ҹдёҖзҡ„ HTTP е®ўжҲ·з«ҜеҹәзЎҖи®ҫж–ҪпјҢж”ҜжҢҒжҺ§еҲ¶йқўе’Ңж•°жҚ®йқўзҡ„ HTTP йҖҡдҝЎпјҢеҢ…жӢ¬иҝһжҺҘжұ з®ЎзҗҶгҖҒи¶…ж—¶й…ҚзҪ®гҖҒдјҡиҜқз®ЎзҗҶе’Ңй”ҷиҜҜеӨ„зҗҶгҖӮ\n\n---\n\n## Requirements\n\n### Requirement: HTTP Session еҲӣе»әдёҺиҝһжҺҘжұ \n\nзі»з»ҹеә”дҪҝз”Ё `requests.Session` й…ҚеҗҲ `HTTPAdapter` е®һзҺ°иҝһжҺҘжұ еӨҚз”ЁпјҢж”ҜжҢҒиҮӘе®ҡд№үиҝһжҺҘжұ еӨ§е°ҸгҖӮ\n\n#### Scenario: й»ҳи®ӨиҝһжҺҘжұ й…ҚзҪ®\n\n- **GIVEN** и°ғз”Ё `create_session()` дёҚдј е…ҘеҸӮж•°\n- **WHEN** еҲӣе»ә HTTP session\n- **THEN** зі»з»ҹ SHALL дёә `http://` е’Ң `https://` дёӨдёӘ scheme еҗ„жҢӮиҪҪдёҖдёӘ `HTTPAdapter`пјҢиҝһжҺҘжұ еҸӮж•°дёә `pool_connections=10`, `pool_maxsize=10`\n\n#### Scenario: иҮӘе®ҡд№үиҝһжҺҘжұ й…ҚзҪ®\n\n- **GIVEN** и°ғз”Ё `create_session(pool_connections=20, pool_maxsize=30)`\n- **WHEN** еҲӣе»ә HTTP session\n- **THEN** зі»з»ҹ SHALL дҪҝз”ЁжҢҮе®ҡзҡ„еҸӮж•°еҲӣе»ә `HTTPAdapter` е№¶жҢӮиҪҪеҲ°дёӨдёӘ scheme\n\n#### Scenario: Session иҝ”еӣһзұ»еһӢ\n\n- **GIVEN** `create_session()` иў«и°ғз”Ё\n- **WHEN** еҮҪж•°иҝ”еӣһ\n- **THEN** иҝ”еӣһеҖј SHALL жҳҜ `requests.Session` е®һдҫӢ\n\n---\n\n### Requirement: Control Plane HTTP е®ўжҲ·з«Ҝ\n\nзі»з»ҹеә”е®һзҺ° `ControlPlaneClient` ж”ҜжҢҒ Workload Manager зҡ„дјҡиҜқз®ЎзҗҶ APIгҖӮ\n\n#### Scenario: еҲӣе»әдјҡиҜқиҜ·жұӮ\n\n- **GIVEN** `ControlPlaneClient` е®һдҫӢе·ІеҲқе§ӢеҢ–пјҢдё”жңүжңүж•Ҳзҡ„ `auth_token`\n- **WHEN** и°ғз”Ё `create_session(name=\"test\", namespace=\"default\", ttl=3600)`\n- **THEN** зі»з»ҹ SHALL еҸ‘йҖҒ `POST {base_url}/v1/code-interpreter` иҜ·жұӮпјҢеҢ…еҗ«пјҡ\n  - Header `Content-Type: application/json`\n  - Header `Authorization: Bearer {token}`\n  - JSON body `{\"name\": \"test\", \"namespace\": \"default\", \"ttl\": 3600, \"metadata\": null}`\n  - и¶…ж—¶ `(connect_timeout, timeout)` й»ҳи®Ө `(5.0, 120)`\n- **AND** иҝ”еӣһе“Қеә”дёӯзҡ„ `data[\"sessionId\"]`\n- **AND** иӢҘе“Қеә”зјәе°‘ `sessionId` еҲҷжҠӣеҮә `ValueError`\n\n#### Scenario: еҲӣе»әдјҡиҜқеёҰ metadata\n\n- **GIVEN** и°ғз”Ё `create_session(name=\"test\", namespace=\"default\", metadata={\"key\": \"value\"}, ttl=3600)`\n- **WHEN** еҸ‘йҖҒиҜ·жұӮ\n- **THEN** JSON body SHALL еҢ…еҗ« `metadata: {\"key\": \"value\"}`\n\n#### Scenario: еҲ йҷӨдјҡиҜқ - жҲҗеҠҹ\n\n- **GIVEN** `session_id` еӯҳеңЁдё”жңүж•Ҳ\n- **WHEN** и°ғз”Ё `delete_session(session_id)`\n- **THEN** зі»з»ҹ SHALL еҸ‘йҖҒ `DELETE {base_url}/v1/code-interpreter/sessions/{session_id}`\n- **AND** иҝ”еӣһ `True`\n\n#### Scenario: еҲ йҷӨдјҡиҜқ - 404 и§ҶдёәжҲҗеҠҹ\n\n- **GIVEN** `session_id` дёҚеӯҳеңЁ\n- **WHEN** жңҚеҠЎз«Ҝиҝ”еӣһ 404\n- **THEN** зі»з»ҹ SHALL иҝ”еӣһ `True`пјҲиҖҢйқһжҠӣеҮәејӮеёёпјү\n\n#### Scenario: еҲ йҷӨдјҡиҜқ - е…¶д»–й”ҷиҜҜ\n\n- **GIVEN** жңҚеҠЎз«Ҝиҝ”еӣһйқһ 2xx/404 й”ҷиҜҜ\n- **WHEN** `delete_session` жү§иЎҢ\n- **THEN** зі»з»ҹ SHALL и®°еҪ•иӯҰе‘Ҡж—Ҙеҝ—\n- **AND** иҝ”еӣһ `False`\n\n#### Scenario: Workload Manager URL и§Јжһҗ\n\n- **GIVEN** жһ„йҖ еҮҪж•°жңӘдј е…Ҙ `workload_manager_url`\n- **WHEN** еҲқе§ӢеҢ– `ControlPlaneClient`\n- **THEN** `base_url` SHALL д»ҺзҺҜеўғеҸҳйҮҸ `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL` иҺ·еҸ–\n\n#### Scenario: Workload Manager URL жҳҫејҸдј е…Ҙ\n\n- **GIVEN** жһ„йҖ еҮҪж•°дј е…Ҙ `workload_manager_url=\"https://wm.example.com\"`\n- **WHEN** еҲқе§ӢеҢ– `ControlPlaneClient`\n- **THEN** `base_url` SHALL дҪҝз”Ёдј е…Ҙзҡ„еҖј\n\n#### Scenario: Auth Token и§Јжһҗ - еҸӮж•°дјҳе…Ҳ\n\n- **GIVEN** жһ„йҖ еҮҪж•°дј е…Ҙ `auth_token=\"my-token\"`\n- **WHEN** еҲқе§ӢеҢ– `ControlPlaneClient`\n- **THEN** зі»з»ҹ SHALL дҪҝз”Ёдј е…Ҙзҡ„ tokenпјҢи®ҫзҪ®й»ҳи®Ө header `Authorization: Bearer my-token`\n\n#### Scenario: Auth Token и§Јжһҗ - д»Һж–Үд»¶иҜ»еҸ–\n\n- **GIVEN** жһ„йҖ еҮҪж•°жңӘдј е…Ҙ `auth_token`\n- **AND** ж–Үд»¶ `/var/run/secrets/kubernetes.io/serviceaccount/token` еӯҳеңЁдё”еҢ…еҗ« `sa-token`\n- **WHEN** еҲқе§ӢеҢ– `ControlPlaneClient`\n- **THEN** зі»з»ҹ SHALL и°ғз”Ё `read_token_from_file` иҜ»еҸ– token\n- **AND** и®ҫзҪ®й»ҳи®Ө header `Authorization: Bearer sa-token`\n\n#### Scenario: Auth Token дёәз©ә - ж—  Authorization header\n\n- **GIVEN** жһ„йҖ еҮҪж•°жңӘдј е…Ҙ `auth_token`\n- **AND** token ж–Үд»¶дёҚеӯҳеңЁжҲ–дёәз©ә\n- **WHEN** еҲқе§ӢеҢ– `ControlPlaneClient`\n- **THEN** зі»з»ҹ SHALL NOT и®ҫзҪ® `Authorization` header\n\n#### Scenario: Close ж–№жі•\n\n- **GIVEN** `ControlPlaneClient` жңүжҙ»и·ғзҡ„ HTTP session\n- **WHEN** и°ғз”Ё `client.close()`\n- **THEN** зі»з»ҹ SHALL е…ій—ӯеә•еұӮзҡ„ `requests.Session`\n\n---\n\n### Requirement: Code Interpreter Data Plane HTTP е®ўжҲ·з«Ҝ\n\nзі»з»ҹеә”е®һзҺ° `CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient` ж”ҜжҢҒ Router д»ЈзҗҶзҡ„д»Јз Ғжү§иЎҢе’Ңж–Үд»¶ж“ҚдҪң APIгҖӮ\n\n#### Scenario: Base URL жһ„е»ә - д»ҺеҸӮж•°\n\n- **GIVEN** жһ„йҖ ж—¶дј е…Ҙ `base_url=\"https://router.example.com/path/\"`\n- **WHEN** еҲқе§ӢеҢ–е®ўжҲ·з«Ҝ\n- **THEN** `self.base_url` SHALL зӣҙжҺҘдҪҝз”Ёдј е…Ҙзҡ„ `base_url`\n\n#### Scenario: Base URL жһ„е»ә - д»Һ router_url е’Ң cr_name\n\n- **GIVEN** жһ„йҖ ж—¶дј е…Ҙ `router_url=\"https://router.example.com\"`, `namespace=\"prod\"`, `cr_name=\"my-interpreter\"`\n- **AND** жңӘдј е…Ҙ `base_url`\n- **WHEN** еҲқе§ӢеҢ–е®ўжҲ·з«Ҝ\n- **THEN** `self.base_url` SHALL дёә `urljoin(router_url, \"/v1/namespaces/prod/code-interpreters/my-interpreter/invocations/\")`\n\n#### Scenario: дјҡиҜқеӨҙи®ҫзҪ®\n\n- **GIVEN** `CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient` е·ІеҲқе§ӢеҢ–пјҢ`session_id` дёә `\"abc123\"`\n- **WHEN** еҸ‘йҖҒд»»ж„Ҹ HTTP иҜ·жұӮ\n- **THEN** иҜ·жұӮ SHALL еҢ…еҗ« header `x-agentcube-session-id: abc123`\n\n#### Scenario: жү§иЎҢе‘Ҫд»ӨиҜ·жұӮ\n\n- **GIVEN** и°ғз”Ё `execute_command(\"ls -la\", timeout=30)`\n- **WHEN** еҸ‘йҖҒиҜ·жұӮ\n- **THEN** зі»з»ҹ SHALL `POST {base_url}api/execute`\n- **AND** body дёә JSON `{\"command\": [\"ls\", \"-la\"], \"timeout\": \"30s\"}`\n- **AND** read timeout дёә `30 + 2.0 = 32.0` з§’пјҲзј“еҶІ 2 з§’йҒҝе…Қ ReadTimeoutпјү\n\n#### Scenario: жү§иЎҢе‘Ҫд»Ө - еӯ—з¬ҰдёІиҪ¬ж•°з»„\n\n- **GIVEN** и°ғз”Ё `execute_command(\"ls -la\")` (еӯ—з¬ҰдёІеҸӮж•°)\n- **WHEN** жһ„йҖ иҜ·жұӮ body\n- **THEN** `command` SHALL иў«иҪ¬жҚўдёә `[\"ls\", \"-la\"]`\n\n#### Scenario: жү§иЎҢе‘Ҫд»Ө - ж•°з»„еҸӮж•°\n\n- **GIVEN** и°ғз”Ё `execute_command([\"ls\", \"-la\"])` (ж•°з»„еҸӮж•°)\n- **WHEN** жһ„йҖ иҜ·жұӮ body\n- **THEN** `command` SHALL зӣҙжҺҘдҪҝз”Ё `[\"ls\", \"-la\"]`\n\n#### Scenario: жү§иЎҢе‘Ҫд»Ө - й»ҳи®Өи¶…ж—¶\n\n- **GIVEN** и°ғз”Ё `execute_command(\"ls\")` жңӘжҢҮе®ҡ timeout\n- **AND** е®ўжҲ·з«Ҝй»ҳи®Ө `timeout=120`\n- **WHEN** жһ„йҖ иҜ·жұӮ\n- **THEN** body дёӯ `timeout` SHALL дёә `\"120s\"`\n- **AND** read timeout SHALL дёә `120 + 2.0 = 122.0` з§’\n\n#### Scenario: жү§иЎҢе‘Ҫд»Ө - йқһйӣ¶йҖҖеҮәз Ғ\n\n- **GIVEN** иҝңзЁӢе‘Ҫд»Өиҝ”еӣһ JSON `{\"exit_code\": 1, \"stderr\": \"error output\", \"stdout\": \"\"}`\n- **WHEN** и§Јжһҗе“Қеә”\n- **THEN** зі»з»ҹ SHALL жҠӣеҮә `CommandExecutionError`пјҢеҢ…еҗ« `exit_code=1`, `stderr=\"error output\"`, `command`\n\n#### Scenario: жү§иЎҢе‘Ҫд»Ө - жҲҗеҠҹ\n\n- **GIVEN** иҝңзЁӢе‘Ҫд»Өиҝ”еӣһ JSON `{\"exit_code\": 0, \"stdout\": \"file1\\nfile2\", \"stderr\": \"\"}`\n- **WHEN** и§Јжһҗе“Қеә”\n- **THEN** зі»з»ҹ SHALL иҝ”еӣһ `\"file1\\nfile2\"`\n\n#### Scenario: еҶҷж–Үд»¶иҜ·жұӮ\n\n- **GIVEN** и°ғз”Ё `write_file(\"hello world\", \"/tmp/test.txt\")`\n- **WHEN** еҸ‘йҖҒиҜ·жұӮ\n- **THEN** зі»з»ҹ SHALL `POST {base_url}api/files`\n- **AND** body дёә JSON `{\"path\": \"/tmp/test.txt\", \"content\": \"aGVsbG8gd29ybGQ=\" (base64), \"mode\": \"0644\"}`\n- **AND** header `Content-Type: application/json`\n\n#### Scenario: еҶҷж–Үд»¶ - base64 зј–з Ғ\n\n- **GIVEN** `content` дёә UTF-8 еӯ—з¬ҰдёІ\n- **WHEN** жһ„йҖ иҜ·жұӮ body\n- **THEN** `content` SHALL е…Ҳзј–з Ғдёә UTF-8 еӯ—иҠӮпјҢеҶҚ base64 зј–з Ғдёәеӯ—з¬ҰдёІ\n\n#### Scenario: дёҠдј ж–Үд»¶иҜ·жұӮ\n\n- **GIVEN** и°ғз”Ё `upload_file(\"/local/file.txt\", \"/remote/file.txt\")`\n- **AND** жң¬ең°ж–Үд»¶еӯҳеңЁ\n- **WHEN** еҸ‘йҖҒиҜ·жұӮ\n- **THEN** зі»з»ҹ SHALL `POST {base_url}api/files` (multipart/form-data)\n- **AND** еҢ…еҗ« `files={'file': <file content>}`\n- **AND** еҢ…еҗ« `data={'path': '/remote/file.txt', 'mode': '0644'}`\n- **AND** header еҢ…еҗ« `x-agentcube-session-id`\n- **AND** дёҚи®ҫзҪ® JSON Content-TypeпјҲеӣ дёәжҳҜ multipartпјү\n\n#### Scenario: дёҠдј ж–Үд»¶ - ж–Үд»¶дёҚеӯҳеңЁ\n\n- **GIVEN** жң¬ең°ж–Үд»¶ `/nonexistent/file.txt` дёҚеӯҳеңЁ\n- **WHEN** и°ғз”Ё `upload_file(\"/nonexistent/file.txt\", \"/remote/file.txt\")`\n- **THEN** зі»з»ҹ SHALL жҠӣеҮә `FileNotFoundError`\n\n#### Scenario: дёӢиҪҪж–Үд»¶иҜ·жұӮ\n\n- **GIVEN** и°ғз”Ё `download_file(\"/remote/file.txt\", \"/local/file.txt\")`\n- **WHEN** еҸ‘йҖҒиҜ·жұӮ\n- **THEN** зі»з»ҹ SHALL `GET {base_url}api/files/remote/file.txt` (еҺ»йҷӨеүҚеҜј `/`)\n- **AND** и®ҫзҪ® `stream=True`\n- **AND** е°Ҷе“Қеә”еҶ…е®№еҶҷе…Ҙжң¬ең°и·Ҝеҫ„ `/local/file.txt`\n\n#### Scenario: дёӢиҪҪж–Үд»¶ - еҲӣе»әзҲ¶зӣ®еҪ•\n\n- **GIVEN** и°ғз”Ё `download_file(\"/remote/file.txt\", \"/local/subdir/file.txt\")`\n- **AND** `/local/subdir/` зӣ®еҪ•дёҚеӯҳеңЁ\n- **WHEN** еҶҷе…Ҙж–Үд»¶\n- **THEN** зі»з»ҹ SHALL еҲӣе»әзҲ¶зӣ®еҪ• `/local/subdir/`\n\n#### Scenario: еҲ—еҮәж–Үд»¶иҜ·жұӮ\n\n- **GIVEN** и°ғз”Ё `list_files(\"/home\")`\n- **WHEN** еҸ‘йҖҒиҜ·жұӮ\n- **THEN** зі»з»ҹ SHALL `GET {base_url}api/files` е№¶еёҰдёҠ query еҸӮж•° `path=/home`\n\n#### Scenario: еҲ—еҮәж–Үд»¶ - й»ҳи®Өи·Ҝеҫ„\n\n- **GIVEN** и°ғз”Ё `list_files()` жңӘдј е…ҘеҸӮж•°\n- **WHEN** еҸ‘йҖҒиҜ·жұӮ\n- **THEN** query еҸӮж•° `path` SHALL й»ҳи®Өдёә `\".\"`\n\n#### Scenario: Close ж–№жі•\n\n- **GIVEN** `CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient` жңүжҙ»и·ғзҡ„ HTTP session\n- **WHEN** и°ғз”Ё `client.close()`\n- **THEN** зі»з»ҹ SHALL е…ій—ӯеә•еұӮзҡ„ `requests.Session`\n\n---\n\n### Requirement: Agent Runtime Data Plane HTTP е®ўжҲ·з«Ҝ\n\nзі»з»ҹеә”е®һзҺ° `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient` ж”ҜжҢҒйҖҡиҝҮ Router и°ғз”Ё Agent RuntimeгҖӮ\n\n#### Scenario: Base URL жһ„е»ә\n\n- **GIVEN** жһ„йҖ ж—¶дј е…Ҙ `router_url=\"https://router.example.com\"`, `namespace=\"prod\"`, `agent_name=\"my-agent\"`\n- **WHEN** еҲқе§ӢеҢ–е®ўжҲ·з«Ҝ\n- **THEN** `self.base_url` SHALL дёә `urljoin(router_url, \"/v1/namespaces/prod/agent-runtimes/my-agent/invocations/\")`\n\n#### Scenario: Bootstrap Session ID - жҲҗеҠҹ\n\n- **GIVEN** `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient` еҲқе§ӢеҢ–е®ҢжҲҗ\n- **WHEN** и°ғз”Ё `bootstrap_session_id()`\n- **THEN** зі»з»ҹ SHALL `GET {base_url}` (ж— йўқеӨ–и·Ҝеҫ„)\n- **AND** д»Һе“Қеә” header `x-agentcube-session-id` иҺ·еҸ–е№¶иҝ”еӣһ session id\n\n#### Scenario: Bootstrap Session ID - зјәеӨұ header\n\n- **GIVEN** bootstrap `GET` иҜ·жұӮжҲҗеҠҹдҪҶе“Қеә” header дёӯжІЎжңү `x-agentcube-session-id`\n- **WHEN** е°қиҜ•жҸҗеҸ– session id\n- **THEN** зі»з»ҹ SHALL жҠӣеҮә `ValueError(\"Missing required response header: x-agentcube-session-id\")`\n\n#### Scenario: Invoke иҜ·жұӮ\n\n- **GIVEN** `session_id` дёә `\"sess-123\"`\n- **WHEN** и°ғз”Ё `invoke(session_id, {\"input\": \"test\"}, timeout=60)`\n- **THEN** зі»з»ҹ SHALL `POST {base_url}`\n- **AND** headers еҢ…еҗ« `x-agentcube-session-id: sess-123`\n- **AND** headers еҢ…еҗ« `Content-Type: application/json`\n- **AND** body дёә JSON `{\"input\": \"test\"}`\n- **AND** и¶…ж—¶дёә `(connect_timeout, 60)` й»ҳи®Ө `(5.0, 60)`\n\n#### Scenario: Invoke ж—  session_id\n\n- **GIVEN** `session_id` дёә `None` жҲ–з©әеӯ—з¬ҰдёІ\n- **WHEN** и°ғз”Ё `invoke(session_id, payload)`\n- **THEN** зі»з»ҹ SHALL жҠӣеҮә `ValueError(\"AgentRuntime session_id is not initialized\")`\n\n#### Scenario: Invoke иҝ”еӣһ Response еҜ№иұЎ\n\n- **GIVEN** `invoke` иҜ·жұӮжҲҗеҠҹ\n- **WHEN** еҮҪж•°иҝ”еӣһ\n- **THEN** зі»з»ҹ SHALL иҝ”еӣһ `requests.Response` еҜ№иұЎпјҲз”ұи°ғз”Ёж–№и§Јжһҗ JSONпјү\n\n#### Scenario: Session Header еёёйҮҸ\n\n- **GIVEN** `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient` зұ»е®ҡд№ү\n- **WHEN** жЈҖжҹҘзұ»еұһжҖ§\n- **THEN** `SESSION_HEADER = \"x-agentcube-session-id\"` SHALL е®ҡд№үдёәзұ»еёёйҮҸ\n\n#### Scenario: Close ж–№жі•\n\n- **GIVEN** `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient` жңүжҙ»и·ғзҡ„ HTTP session\n- **WHEN** и°ғз”Ё `client.close()`\n- **THEN** зі»з»ҹ SHALL е…ій—ӯеә•еұӮзҡ„ `requests.Session`\n\n---\n\n### Requirement: и¶…ж—¶й…ҚзҪ®з»ҹдёҖ\n\nзі»з»ҹеә”ж”ҜжҢҒз»ҹдёҖзҡ„и¶…ж—¶й…ҚзҪ®пјҢй»ҳи®ӨиҜ»и¶…ж—¶ 120 з§’пјҢиҝһжҺҘи¶…ж—¶ 5 з§’гҖӮ\n\n#### Scenario: Control Plane й»ҳи®Өи¶…ж—¶\n\n- **GIVEN** `ControlPlaneClient` дҪҝз”Ёй»ҳи®ӨеҸӮж•°жһ„йҖ \n- **WHEN** еҸ‘йҖҒд»»ж„ҸиҜ·жұӮ\n- **THEN** и¶…ж—¶ SHALL дёә `(5.0, 120)` (connect_timeout, read_timeout)\n\n#### Scenario: Code Interpreter Data Plane й»ҳи®Өи¶…ж—¶\n\n- **GIVEN** `CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient` дҪҝз”Ёй»ҳи®ӨеҸӮж•°жһ„йҖ \n- **WHEN** еҸ‘йҖҒд»»ж„ҸиҜ·жұӮ\n- **THEN** й»ҳи®Ө `timeout` SHALL дёә `120`пјҢ`connect_timeout` SHALL дёә `5.0`\n\n#### Scenario: Agent Runtime Data Plane й»ҳи®Өи¶…ж—¶\n\n- **GIVEN** `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient` дҪҝз”Ёй»ҳи®ӨеҸӮж•°жһ„йҖ \n- **WHEN** еҸ‘йҖҒд»»ж„ҸиҜ·жұӮ\n- **THEN** й»ҳи®Ө `timeout` SHALL дёә `120`пјҢ`connect_timeout` SHALL дёә `5.0`\n\n#### Scenario: иҮӘе®ҡд№үи¶…ж—¶\n\n- **GIVEN** жһ„йҖ  `ControlPlaneClient(timeout=60, connect_timeout=3.0)`\n- **WHEN** еҸ‘йҖҒиҜ·жұӮ\n- **THEN** и¶…ж—¶ SHALL дёә `(3.0, 60)`\n\n#### Scenario: Per-call и¶…ж—¶иҰҶзӣ– - execute_command\n\n- **GIVEN** `execute_command(command, timeout=30)`\n- **WHEN** иҜҘи°ғз”Ёжү§иЎҢ\n- **THEN** read timeout SHALL дҪҝз”Ё `30`пјҲеҠ зј“еҶІ 2 з§’еҗҺдёә 32пјүпјҢconnect timeout дҪҝз”Ёе®һдҫӢй»ҳи®ӨеҖј\n\n#### Scenario: Per-call и¶…ж—¶иҰҶзӣ– - invoke\n\n- **GIVEN** `invoke(..., timeout=30.0)`\n- **WHEN** иҜҘи°ғз”Ёжү§иЎҢ\n- **THEN** read timeout SHALL дҪҝз”Ё `30.0`пјҢconnect timeout дҪҝз”Ёе®һдҫӢй»ҳи®ӨеҖј\n\n---\n\n### Requirement: ејӮеёёеұӮж¬Ўз»“жһ„\n\nзі»з»ҹеә”е®ҡд№үжё…жҷ°зҡ„ејӮеёёзұ»еұӮж¬ЎпјҢдҫҝдәҺи°ғз”Ёж–№жҚ•иҺ·е’ҢеӨ„зҗҶй”ҷиҜҜгҖӮ\n\n#### Scenario: ејӮеёёз»§жүҝ\n\n- **GIVEN** ејӮеёёзұ»е®ҡд№үеңЁ `agentcube/exceptions.py`\n- **WHEN** жЈҖжҹҘзұ»еұӮж¬Ў\n- **THEN** `AgentCubeError` SHALL з»§жүҝ `Exception`\n- **AND** `CommandExecutionError` SHALL з»§жүҝ `AgentCubeError`\n- **AND** `SessionError` SHALL з»§жүҝ `AgentCubeError`\n- **AND** `DataPlaneError` SHALL з»§жүҝ `AgentCubeError`\n\n#### Scenario: CommandExecutionError жһ„йҖ \n\n- **GIVEN** иҝңзЁӢе‘Ҫд»Өжү§иЎҢеӨұиҙҘпјҢйҖҖеҮәз Ғдёә 2пјҢstderr дёә \"failed\"пјҢе‘Ҫд»Өдёә \"ls -la\"\n- **WHEN** жһ„йҖ  `CommandExecutionError(2, \"failed\", \"ls -la\")`\n- **THEN** ејӮеёё SHALL еҢ…еҗ«еұһжҖ§ `exit_code=2`, `stderr=\"failed\"`, `command=\"ls -la\"`\n- **AND** ејӮеёёж¶ҲжҒҜ SHALL дёә `\"Command failed (exit 2): failed\"`\n\n#### Scenario: CommandExecutionError й»ҳи®Ө command\n\n- **GIVEN** жһ„йҖ  `CommandExecutionError(1, \"error\")` дёҚдј е…Ҙ command\n- **WHEN** ејӮеёёеҲӣе»ә\n- **THEN** `command` еұһжҖ§ SHALL дёә `None`\n\n#### Scenario: SessionError еҹәзұ»\n\n- **GIVEN** `SessionError` е®ҡд№ү\n- **WHEN** жЈҖжҹҘзұ»е®ҡд№ү\n- **THEN** `SessionError` SHALL дёә `AgentCubeError` зҡ„еӯҗзұ»пјҢж–ҮжЎЈеӯ—з¬ҰдёІдёә \"Raised when session creation or management fails\"\n\n#### Scenario: DataPlaneError еҹәзұ»\n\n- **GIVEN** `DataPlaneError` е®ҡд№ү\n- **WHEN** жЈҖжҹҘзұ»е®ҡд№ү\n- **THEN** `DataPlaneError` SHALL дёә `AgentCubeError` зҡ„еӯҗзұ»пјҢж–ҮжЎЈеӯ—з¬ҰдёІдёә \"Raised when Data Plane operations fail\"\n\n---\n\n### Requirement: Token ж–Үд»¶иҜ»еҸ–\n\nзі»з»ҹеә”ж”ҜжҢҒд»Һж–Үд»¶иҜ»еҸ–и®ӨиҜҒ tokenпјҢеӨ„зҗҶж–Үд»¶дёҚеӯҳеңЁжғ…еҶөгҖӮ\n\n#### Scenario: иҜ»еҸ– token ж–Үд»¶жҲҗеҠҹ\n\n- **GIVEN** ж–Үд»¶ `/path/to/token` еҶ…е®№дёә `\"my-secret-token\\n\"`\n- **WHEN** и°ғз”Ё `read_token_from_file(\"/path/to/token\")`\n- **THEN** иҝ”еӣһ `\"my-secret-token\"` (е·І strip)\n\n#### Scenario: иҜ»еҸ– token ж–Үд»¶ - еӨҡиЎҢ\n\n- **GIVEN** ж–Үд»¶еҶ…е®№дёә `\"token-line1\\ntoken-line2\\n\"`\n- **WHEN** и°ғз”Ё `read_token_from_file`\n- **THEN** иҝ”еӣһ `\"token-line1\\ntoken-line2\"` (д»… strip еүҚеҗҺз©әзҷҪ)\n\n#### Scenario: ж–Үд»¶дёҚеӯҳеңЁ\n\n- **GIVEN** ж–Үд»¶ `/nonexistent/token` дёҚеӯҳеңЁ\n- **WHEN** и°ғз”Ё `read_token_from_file(\"/nonexistent/token\")`\n- **THEN** иҝ”еӣһз©әеӯ—з¬ҰдёІ `\"\"` (дёҚжҠӣеҮәејӮеёё)\n\n#### Scenario: ж–Үд»¶иҜ»еҸ–жқғйҷҗй”ҷиҜҜ\n\n- **GIVEN** ж–Үд»¶еӯҳеңЁдҪҶж— иҜ»еҸ–жқғйҷҗ\n- **WHEN** и°ғз”Ё `read_token_from_file`\n- **THEN** ејӮеёё SHALL еҗ‘дёҠдј ж’ӯпјҲдёҚжҚ•иҺ·пјү\n\n---\n\n### Requirement: ж—Ҙеҝ—е·Ҙе…·\n\nзі»з»ҹеә”жҸҗдҫӣж—Ҙеҝ—е·Ҙе…·еҮҪж•°гҖӮ\n\n#### Scenario: Logger еҲӣе»ә\n\n- **GIVEN** и°ғз”Ё `get_logger(\"agentcube.client\")`\n- **WHEN** еҮҪж•°иҝ”еӣһ\n- **THEN** иҝ”еӣһдёҖдёӘ `logging.Logger` е®һдҫӢпјҢеҗҚз§°дёә `\"agentcube.client\"`\n\n#### Scenario: й»ҳи®Өж—Ҙеҝ—зә§еҲ«\n\n- **GIVEN** и°ғз”Ё `get_logger(\"agentcube.client\")` дёҚдј е…Ҙ level\n- **WHEN** еҲӣе»ә logger\n- **THEN** ж—Ҙеҝ—зә§еҲ« SHALL й»ҳи®Өдёә `logging.INFO`\n\n#### Scenario: иҮӘе®ҡд№үж—Ҙеҝ—зә§еҲ«\n\n- **GIVEN** и°ғз”Ё `get_logger(\"agentcube.client\", level=logging.DEBUG)`\n- **WHEN** еҲӣе»ә logger\n- **THEN** ж—Ҙеҝ—зә§еҲ« SHALL дёә `logging.DEBUG`\n\n#### Scenario: еӯ—з¬ҰдёІж—Ҙеҝ—зә§еҲ«\n\n- **GIVEN** и°ғз”Ё `get_logger(\"agentcube.client\", level=\"DEBUG\")`\n- **WHEN** еҲӣе»ә logger\n- **THEN** зі»з»ҹ SHALL е°Ҷеӯ—з¬ҰдёІ `\"DEBUG\"` иҪ¬жҚўдёә `logging.DEBUG`\n\n---\n\n### Requirement: е…¬е…ұ API еҜјеҮә\n\nзі»з»ҹеә”д»ҺеҢ…ж №еҜјеҮәе…¬е…ұзұ»гҖӮ\n\n#### Scenario: ж №еҢ…еҜјеҮә\n\n- **GIVEN** `from agentcube import CodeInterpreterClient, AgentRuntimeClient`\n- **WHEN** жү§иЎҢеҜје…Ҙ\n- **THEN** `CodeInterpreterClient` е’Ң `AgentRuntimeClient` SHALL еҸҜз”Ё\n\n#### Scenario: clients еӯҗеҢ…еҜјеҮә\n\n- **GIVEN** `from agentcube.clients import ControlPlaneClient, CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient, AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient`\n- **WHEN** жү§иЎҢеҜје…Ҙ\n- **THEN** дёүдёӘзұ» SHALL еҸҜз”Ё\n\n#### Scenario: __all__ е®ҡд№ү\n\n- **GIVEN** `agentcube/__init__.py` ж–Үд»¶\n- **WHEN** жЈҖжҹҘ `__all__`\n- **THEN** `__all__` SHALL еҢ…еҗ« `[\"CodeInterpreterClient\", \"AgentRuntimeClient\"]`\n\n#### Scenario: clients __all__ е®ҡд№ү\n\n- **GIVEN** `agentcube/clients/__init__.py` ж–Үд»¶\n- **WHEN** жЈҖжҹҘ `__all__`\n- **THEN** `__all__` SHALL еҢ…еҗ« `[\"ControlPlaneClient\", \"CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient\", \"AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient\"]`\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Files\n\n| File | Purpose |\n|------|---------|\n| `agentcube/utils/http.py` | `create_session` еҮҪж•° |\n| `agentcube/utils/utils.py` | `read_token_from_file` еҮҪж•° |\n| `agentcube/utils/log.py` | `get_logger` еҮҪж•° |\n| `agentcube/utils/__init__.py` | е·Ҙе…·жЁЎеқ—ж Үи®° |\n| `agentcube/exceptions.py` | ејӮеёёзұ»е®ҡд№ү |\n| `agentcube/clients/control_plane.py` | `ControlPlaneClient` зұ» |\n| `agentcube/clients/code_interpreter_data_plane.py` | `CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient` зұ» |\n| `agentcube/clients/agent_runtime_data_plane.py` | `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient` зұ» |\n| `agentcube/clients/__init__.py` | е®ўжҲ·з«ҜеҜјеҮә |\n| `agentcube/__init__.py` | еҢ…ж №еҜјеҮә |\n\n---\n\n## Dependencies\n\n| Package | Purpose |\n|---------|---------|\n| `requests` | HTTP е®ўжҲ·з«Ҝ |\n| `PyJWT>=2.0.0` | JWT еӨ„зҗҶпјҲеҰӮйңҖиҰҒпјү |\n| `cryptography` | еҠ еҜҶж”ҜжҢҒпјҲеҰӮйңҖиҰҒпјү |\n\n---\n\n## Validation Checklist\n\n- [ ] `create_session()` еҲӣе»әеёҰ `HTTPAdapter` зҡ„ `requests.Session`\n- [ ] `create_session()` ж”ҜжҢҒиҮӘе®ҡд№ү `pool_connections` е’Ң `pool_maxsize`\n- [ ] `ControlPlaneClient.create_session` POST жӯЈзЎ® JSON body е№¶иҝ”еӣһ `sessionId`\n- [ ] `ControlPlaneClient.delete_session` еҜ№ 404 иҝ”еӣһ `True`\n- [ ] `ControlPlaneClient` д»Һ `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL` иҜ»еҸ– base_url\n- [ ] `ControlPlaneClient` д»ҺеҸӮж•°жҲ–ж–Үд»¶иҜ»еҸ– auth_token\n- [ ] `ControlPlaneClient.close()` е…ій—ӯ session\n- [ ] `CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient` жӯЈзЎ®жһ„е»ә base_url\n- [ ] `CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient` и®ҫзҪ® `x-agentcube-session-id` header\n- [ ] `execute_command` жӯЈзЎ®жһ„йҖ иҜ·жұӮ body е’Ңи¶…ж—¶\n- [ ] `execute_command` еҜ№йқһйӣ¶йҖҖеҮәз ҒжҠӣеҮә `CommandExecutionError`\n- [ ] `write_file` base64 зј–з Ғ content\n- [ ] `upload_file` дҪҝз”Ё multipart/form-data\n- [ ] `download_file` дҪҝз”Ё `stream=True`\n- [ ] `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient.bootstrap_session_id` жҸҗеҸ– header\n- [ ] `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient.invoke` жӯЈзЎ®и®ҫзҪ® headers\n- [ ] `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient.SESSION_HEADER` еёёйҮҸ\n- [ ] и¶…ж—¶й»ҳи®ӨеҖј `(connect_timeout=5.0, timeout=120)`\n- [ ] ејӮеёёзұ»еұӮж¬ЎжӯЈзЎ®\n- [ ] `CommandExecutionError` еҢ…еҗ« `exit_code`, `stderr`, `command`\n- [ ] `read_token_from_file` еҜ№дёҚеӯҳеңЁж–Үд»¶иҝ”еӣһз©әеӯ—з¬ҰдёІ\n- [ ] `get_logger` иҝ”еӣһжӯЈзЎ®е‘ҪеҗҚзҡ„ logger\n- [ ] е…¬е…ұ API д»Һ `agentcube` е’Ң `agentcube.clients` жӯЈзЎ®еҜјеҮә","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/delta-spec.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/delta-spec.md","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775882025193,"end":1775882025267}}}}
